Full Title: McGill Canadian Conf. for Linguistics Undergraduates 
Short Title: McCCLU 

Date: 06-Mar-2009 - 08-Mar-2009
Location: Montreal, QC, Canada 
Contact Person: Kate McCurdy
Meeting Email: mccclu2009@gmail.com
Web Site: http://www.mccclu.com 

Linguistic Field(s): General Linguistics 

Call Deadline: 09-Feb-2009 

Meeting Description:

A forum for undergraduates to share original research relating to linguistics. 

Call for Papers

Undergraduate students interested in participating are encouraged to submit an
abstract for a 20-minute talk with a 10-minute question period on any topic
pertaining to linguistics. Students may also submit an abstract for a poster on
any topic relevant to linguistics at our poster session to be held during the
conference. Abstracts should be a maximum of one-page in length and should be
submitted online to mccclu2009@gmail.com by Monday February 9th, 2009. Please
indicate whether you would like to be considered for a 20-minute talk or for the
poster session or both.



	
